# DPAH (Data Patterns Agents Hub) - Complete Application Documentation

## Executive Summary

DPAH is an **enterprise AI agent orchestration platform** built with FastAPI that provides role-based access control (RBAC) for AI agents across multiple business collections (RMS, SCM, HRMS, FINANCE). The application implements a sophisticated **LangGraph-based workflow** that routes user requests through permission-gated agent nodes (Creator, Reviewer, Approver).

